{"tid":2368011,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"WhatsApp 因劣評如潮而延遲變更私隱政策","createTime":"2021-01-15T20:45:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T09:44:39.000Z","uid":11598,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"97aaa06c5286aeacb9760093faedc94051485bc5","tid":2368011,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T20:45:47.000Z","msg":"WhatsApp 指出受爭議嘅私隱政策更動唔會如期推出，而且最少擱置 3 個月<br />\n估計呢個動作可能係因為用家越嚟越緊張嘅反對聲浪<br />\n<br />\n今日 WhatsApp 最新Blog貼文宣佈將會暫停最近受爭議嘅私隱政策改動。<br />\nWhatsApp 指出需要更多時間去澄清私隱同安全相關嘅錯誤資訊。<br />\n呢個變更將會擱置最少 3 個月，而且暫時未有喺呢段時間入邊再做其他新嘅改動嘅計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">WhatsApp 奶晒噠 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢個動作好明顯係針對最近燒得如火如荼嘅私隱政策更動。本質上，新嘅 WhatsApp 私隱權政策容許該公司將指定用家嘅WhatsApp資料轉移到其他Facebook旗下嘅公司，亦包括同名嘅社交網絡。<br />\n<br />\n對於喺上星期見街嘅私隱政策變更，公眾嘅反應係一面倒反感；而且仲引起咗一大班使用者開始逃離WhatsApp，轉向其他加密即時通訊平台例如 Telegram同 Signal。後者仲一度因為巨量嘅使用者增長造成伺服器癱瘓。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nref: <a href=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/whatsapp-privacy-delay-1193458/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.androidauthority.com%2Fwhatsapp-privacy-delay-1193458%2F&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyEBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=582760e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.androidauthority.com/whatsapp-privacy-delay-1193458/</a><br />\nwhatsapp blog: <a href=\"https://blog.whatsapp.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.whatsapp.com%2F&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyEBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=2e0e9eee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://blog.whatsapp.com/</a>"},{"pid":"9107fda49907d690efe3c771fe63db202c47e6e2","tid":2368011,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T20:47:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>No one will have their account suspended or deleted on February 8.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\naccording to official blog post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04feb8f8acc172994b3e9167f474cff